        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【MWC 2024】Samsung 可捲曲手機    Cling Band 戴手上可感應身體狀況</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/29/cling-band/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=cling-band</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/29/cling-band/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 07:23:01 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Cling Band]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[samsung]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221882</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">萬眾矚目的盛事 MWC 2024 在西班牙巴塞隆拿舉行，Samsung 就率先拋出震撼彈，首次展示了可捲曲螢幕的概念手機 Cling Band，同場亦有可調整螢幕視角以保護私隱的 Flex Magic Pixel。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221890" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/bb1iu3qbimg-694x495.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="495" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/bb1iu3qbimg-694x495.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/bb1iu3qbimg.jpeg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1221883 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/202402281042585fd725-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/202402281042585fd725-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/202402281042585fd725.jpg 1060w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可捲曲螢幕的概念手機 Cling Band</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Cling Band 在未捲曲的情況下，基本上如一般手機無異，惟機背有多個板塊，這種設計方便用家捲曲手機。更有趣的是，Cling Band 可讓用家在捲曲後戴上手上，螢幕在捲曲後大致平順，少許不平。Cling Band 還能透過內建心率感應器紀錄身體活動狀況，但現時 Samsung 尚未透露此概念設計具體細節。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">除了 Cling Band 概念手機外，Samsung 在今年的 MWC 上展示了多款概念手機，包括可調整螢幕視角以保護私隱的 Flex Magic Pixel。</p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/2408672">TVBS</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><p><b>相關文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/18/samsung-s24-%e7%8f%be%e5%a0%b4%e6%b8%ac%e8%a9%a6%e9%96%8b%e7%ae%b1%e3%80%80%e6%b8%af%e4%ba%ba%e6%9c%80%e6%84%9b-7-%e5%a4%a7%e5%8a%9f%e8%83%bd/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Samsung S24 現場測試開箱影片　港人最愛 7 大功能</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/18/samsung-s24-ultra-first-look/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra　外形　手感　AI 功能　操作體驗初步評測</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/29/samsung-know-smart-tv-2024/wireless-home/audio-visual/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Samsung Know 再獲 CC 認證，今年將擴展至智能電視產品</a></li></blockquote><p></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/29/cling-band/mobile-phone/">【MWC 2024】Samsung 可捲曲手機    Cling Band 戴手上可感應身體狀況</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/29/cling-band/mobile-phone/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>《FF7 Rebirth》Sony 印碟擺烏龍印錯標籤，玩家要入「資料碟」來玩</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/29/ff7-rebirth-game-cd-print-failure/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ff7-rebirth-game-cd-print-failure</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/29/ff7-rebirth-game-cd-print-failure/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 05:30:51 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[《FINAL FANTASY VII REBIRTH》]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[FF 7]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Final Fantasy]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[square enix]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221867</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>《FINAL FANTASY VII REBIRTH》在今日正式推出（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/07/final-fantasy-vii-rebirth/game-channel/">相關報道</a>），豈料就在推出前一日，Square Enix 發布緊急公告，表示 SONY 製作過程出錯，致使日本版《FINAL FANTASY VII REBIRTH》 遊戲光碟和數據光碟碟面印刷相反。</p><p>Square Enix 在緊急公告中表示，雖然光碟印刷出錯，但已購買了錯版光碟的玩家仍可遊玩，只是要倒轉放入光碟的次序。Square Enix 公告指，拿到錯版遊戲的玩家需要先將黑色「Play Disc」光碟放入遊戲主機，安裝遊戲內容，跟隨指示完成安裝後，就可以將白色「Data Disc」放入遊戲機遊玩。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221869" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/8238652320c04b9d6ecf-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/8238652320c04b9d6ecf-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/8238652320c04b9d6ecf.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>《FINAL FANTASY VII REBIRTH》早前已推出體驗版，官方表示擁有體驗版保存資料的玩家，可以於正式版領取「咕波幸運符＆冒險道具套組」。咕波幸運符有一定機率使取得材料道具數量增加的配件；而冒險道具套組有治療劑和乙太等，由能在冒險中派上用場的道具組成的套組。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.itmedia.co.jp/news/articles/2402/28/news181.html?fbclid=IwAR2sXCIehFrI2jHsEaZ4BEmt9h2-t-Rp3I_8zyVXz-Q2izQaesors84ON_I">IT Media News</a>、<a href="https://www.jp.square-enix.com/ffvii_rebirth/news/information/17175.html">Square Enix JP</a><br /><b>相關文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/28/final-fantasy-16-echoes-of-the-fallen-reivew/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】《Final Fantasy XVI：Echoes of the Fallen》 歷代最強怪物登場+天空古代遺跡探索</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/04/square-enix-ai/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Square Enix 將積極使用 AI 創作，社長：生成式 AI 提高開發效率</a></li></blockquote><p></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/29/ff7-rebirth-game-cd-print-failure/game-channel/">《FF7 Rebirth》Sony 印碟擺烏龍印錯標籤，玩家要入「資料碟」來玩</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
